Testcase design assignment
Design Test case for saucedemo.com login page

| Test Case ID | Test Description                                       | Pre-Condition                           | Test Input                                                  | Test Data                                             | Expected Result                                                         |

| TC_Login_01  | Verify login with valid credentials                    | User is on SauceDemo login page         | Enter valid username and password. Click Login              | Username: standard_user Password: secret_sauce        | User should be successfully logged in and redirected to Products page   |
| TC_Login_02  | Verify login with invalid username                     | User is on login page                   | Enter invalid username and valid password. Click Login      | Username: invalid_user  Password: secret_sauce        | Error message displayed: "Username and password do not match any user"  |
| TC_Login_03  | Verify login with invalid password                     | User is on login page                   | Enter valid username and invalid password. Click Login      | Username: standard_user Password: wrong_password      | Error message displayed                                                 |
| TC_Login_04  | Verify login with blank username                       | User is on login page                   | Leave username blank, enter password. Click Login           | Username: (Blank)       Password: secret_sauce        | Error message displayed: "Username is required"                         |
| TC_Login_05  | Verify login with blank password                       | User is on login page                   | Enter username, leave password blank. Click Login           | Username: standard_user Password: (Blank)             | Error message displayed: "Password is required"                         |
| TC_Login_06  | Verify login with both fields blank                    | User is on login page                   | Leave username and password blank. Click Login              | Username: (Blank)       Password: (Blank)             | Error message displayed: "Username is required"                         |
| TC_Login_07  | Verify username field case sensitivity                 | User is on login page                   | Enter username in uppercase and valid password. Click Login | Username: STANDARD_USER Password: secret_sauce        | Error message displayed (Username is case-sensitive)                    |
| TC_Login_08  | Verify login using Enter key                           | User is on login page                   | Enter valid credentials and press Enter key                 | Username: standard_user Password: secret_sauce        | User should be logged in successfully                                   |
